    {
      "id": "PopularPost179156",
      "post_content": "It's not for some silly hand-overload deck.  \n  \nIt's not for an [Underworld Dreams](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Underworld Dreams) deck.  \n  \nIt's for that deck with 30 counterspells which needs to just stop the opponent from doing *anything* while it combos out. For that use, it is another copy of [Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell) which also replaces itself. Your opponent's hand size doesn't matter it you're just going to counter everything anyway.  \n  \nIt's not a **good** card, but it has its uses.",
      "posted_by": "Ideatog",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost179156\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">It's not for some silly hand-overload deck.<br/><br/>It's not for an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Underworld Dreams\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Underworld Dreams\">Underworld Dreams</a> deck.<br/><br/>It's for that deck with 30 counterspells which needs to just stop the opponent from doing <i>anything</i> while it combos out. For that use, it is another copy of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Counterspell\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell\">Counterspell</a> which also replaces itself. Your opponent's hand size doesn't matter it you're just going to counter everything anyway.<br/><br/>It's not a <b>good</b> card, but it has its uses.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '179156'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2063\">Ideatog</span>\r\n                                (7/14/2011 11:27:43 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubCo